---
title: Grain, Salmon and Kale Harvest Super Salad with Spiced Sweet Potatoes
description: This nutty wild rice salad is the perfect combination of salty, sticky, sweet and crunchy. Salmon, roasted sweet potatoes and crisp chopped apples complete this stand-out supper salad.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/salade-sante-de-chou-frise-de-saumon-et-de-cereales-61278760.jpg
